_sText:
Hey,

I present you my new map.

bhop\_fly\_fracture

This map is for legithop (100aa, 100tick).

There are 3 levels and 1 bonus stage. It's a short map.

It's an easy/medium map. I think that everybody can finish it.

I would like to thank Dotty, Keyuu and Hoover, who helped me a lot with the soundscapes and VHE.

As I said for my first Flymap, I created a group for people who love flymap:
[FlyBhopper](http://steamcommunity.com/groups/flybhopbest "FlyBhopper")

KingDeppy.

Bye.
